race.description: Ladbrokes Srm In Multis Maiden Plate
race.comment: REGENERATION (7) returned last time with a solid second at Sale over 1200m after being prominent at the bend. Needs to be at his best to beat this field but he deserves his chance. MERIMBULA (6) didn't hit the mark when highly-fancied in two runs in the debut campaign, but was far from disgraced and has looked good in a couple of Mornington jumpouts in preparation for the return. TSAVO (8) resumed from a spell last start with a sound third over 1000m at Bendigo when he made late ground. Must raise the bar but he has the talent to test this line-up. VALEDICTORIAN (9) is ready to break through after collecting his 4th minor placing in a row last time over 1000m at Cranbourne. Should camp just off the leaders. Meets some better types this time but he has the talent to test this line-up.
